CatDescriptText: image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 12, 1941, pg. 10, reads: The Guests Has A Grand Time At The Golf Tourney...And Looked Pretty, Too - The sun shone and the guests were pleased and pleasing at the Eastern Open Golf Tournament in Pittsburgh last weekend. Courier photoman snapped these charming folks (left to right); Mrs. Jackie Murray..."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Jackie Murray wearing floral dress and wide brimmed hat and holding golf trophy, seated with legs crossed on counter
